headline: Bullish Bets on Warner Bros. Shares Hit Record Volumes
summary: Options traders are piling into bullish wagers on Warner Bros. Discovery after The Wall Street Journal reported that Paramount Skydance is preparing a bid for the company. More than 399,000 call options tied to the entertainment company changed hands on Thursday, a record, show Cboe Global Markets data.
